: 1575563857, "last_modified": 1651222230}, "last_reply_by": "Bijiabo", "last_touched": 1668358512, "title": "为什么国外人做事会有一种传承感? 还是国内的太浮躁了?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/894894", "created": 1668331738, "deleted": 0, "content": "俺有举几个方面的例子吧\r\n\r\n1. 书籍: 你会看到很多经典的书都修订到 2 位数的版本了\r\n2. 汽车: 比如奥迪某款车型, 能看到家族风格\r\n3. 软件: 比如 windows, macos\r\n\r\n\r\n而国内做的东西吧... 虽然感觉不错, 但似乎就没有传承, 给人感觉就不能坚持个几十年在一件事上精进?\r\n\r\n这是为啥? 是文化原因? 还是民族性格?", "content_rendered": "<p>俺有举几个方面的例子吧</p>\n<ol>\n<li>书籍: 你会看到很多经典的书都修订到 2 位数的版本了</li>\n<li>汽车: 比如奥迪某款车型, 能看到家族风格</li>\n<li>软件: 比如 windows, macos</li>\n</ol>\n<p>而国内做的东西吧... 虽然感觉不错, 但似乎就没有传承, 给人感觉就不能坚持个几十年在一件事上精进?</p>\n<p>这是为啥? 是文化原因? 还是民族性格?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1668331738, "replies": 63, "id": 894894}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 192898, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3615, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 598304, "username": "RATIONALITY", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/RATIONALITY", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d162001116c136cabeadb1577fd4e2c9?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d162001116c136cabeadb1577fd4e2c9?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d162001116c136cabeadb1577fd4e2c9?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1666259235, "last_modified": 1666341655}, "last_reply_by": "testver", "last_touched": 1668348179, "title": "求问五年内最稳的 4%收益方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/894842", "created": 1668312197, "deleted": 0, "content": "资金高于各银行大额存单门槛，低